<BaseLayout
  title="MOJ vs Certified Translation Dubai | Guide"
  description="Need an official translation in the UAE? Learn the difference between certified translation and legal translation (MOJ), when attestation is needed, and which translation service is accepted by courts, embassies, and government agencies in Dubai."
